OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry night with clear spells to start,
OL,7,Fcloud generally thickening as the
OL,8,Fnight progresses with perhaps a few
OL,9,Foutbreaks of rain developing towards
OL,10,Fdawn, with a low risk of heavy bursts
OL,11,Fand thunder. Winds will remain
OL,12,Fgenerally light.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FAny cloud and rain should
OL,15,Fclear during the morning to give a
OL,16,Fbright, sunny and hot day. Staying a
OL,17,Flittle cooler along the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
